»CL8:        Where, When, How Much?
»CL9:-------------------------------------

»CL0:The »CL1:RTS» will be held in »CL1:Seyssins»
which is located in »CL1:Isere» (France) on
the 5,6, and 7 September 1998.

The doors will open on Saturday, the
5th of September at 08h00 and will be
closed on Monday, the 7th of
September at 20h00.





»CL8:LOCATION:»

»CL1:"Salle polyvalente Le PRISME"»
(prism-shaped polyvalent hall)
located in »CL1:Seyssins» near »CL1:Grenoble».
»CL1:A48» highway, »CL1:Seyssins» exit, then
follow the signs to the big free car
park of the hall.

»CL8:MEANS OF ACCESS:»

»CL1:By car:»

For those coming from the North:
Go in the direction of »CL1:LYON», then in
the direction of »CL1:GRENOBLE» on the A48
highway, then B48.



For those coming from the South:
Go in the direction of »CL1:LYON», then A7
highway to »CL1:VALENCE», then A480 highway
to »CL1:GRENOBLE».

For those coming from the East:
Go in the direction of »CL1:GRENOBLE», on
the A41 highway, then "Rocade Sud"
till the end (in the direction of
Seyssins).

»CL1:By train:

Arrival at »CL1:GRENOBLE» railway station,
then take the shuttle to the »CL1:RTS» (the
timetable will be given later on the
RTS web page or on request).



»CL1:By plane:»

International Airport of
»CL1:Lyon/Satolas», then bus (»CL1:Satobus») to
»CL1:GRENOBLE» coach station. Finally, take
the »CL1:RTS» shuttle from the nearby
railway station.

»CL1:By canoe kayak:» (»CL8:-hehe -CTN»)

Return To the Source of the »CL1:Drac» by
the »CL1:Isere» river and paddle to the
next floating phonebox labelled
"»CL1:RTS»". Finally, launch 2 »CLA:flares»...
»CLA:Here we come!»

The »CL1:RTS» is (almost) free ;-)



If you pre-register, the price is
»CL1:70FF». On the spot, it is »CL1:100FF» for
boys and transsexuals, for the whole
event.

      »CL9: ---»CL8:  FREE FOR GIRLS! »CL9:---

