»CL8:Life at the RTS:»

Capacity of over 500 people with
their machine(s).

Bar open 24h a day, with drinks,
sandwichs, etc... at low prices.

Big car park for everyone.

Phonebox in the hall.

Toilets.


»CL1:HIFI-VIDEO EQUIPEMENT:»

2 big screens.
Professional HIFI equipement.

»CL1:NETWORK:»

Internal network(not the one of your
neurons: bring your RJ45 cables).

»CL1:RULES:»

Any competing person must be present
at the party.

Every presented production will be
spread after the competition.

No alcohol.

No cigarettes.

No drugs (winners don't use drugs).

No illegal software.

No disturbing people.

No over-powerfull sono.

No electricity over-consuming devices
(hot plate, etc...).

Long live the old machines - Return
To the Source Rulez. 